# AI Context (token-disciplined)

Project: Go `rc` result-check utility.

Behavior contract:
- Compare expected code vs actual code.
- Emit SUCCESS on match, ERROR on mismatch.
- Honor `KILL` behavior (exit with actual code when mismatch).
- Keep shell wrapper compatibility (`rc.sh`).

Dependencies:
- Prefer `loggerx` output when available, fallback output otherwise.

Token efficiency rules:
- Keep under ~140 words.
- Include only active constraints and migration-critical notes.
- Store design history in `.ai-history`.
